channel.title: NickScape Development Team (name will be changed soon)
channel.description:
[center][b]INTERNET ONLY WORKS ON LAPTOP UNTILL TUESDAY OF NEXT WEEK.[/b][/center]
[center][b]NickScape Development Team[/b] My Plans for nickscape are to find a suitable name that will be recognized all across the Private Server World. I plan to make nickscape a enjoyable server, and a reliable server, with a homepage, and clients. I plan to have a experienced staff on my side and to have fun with this project. Right now we have a TestScape based server with some editorial practice done to it, to make it more enjoyable. It is currently a hamachi only server, but will be no-ip when i figure out what is wrong. If you would like to be a Coder, you need to have access to hamachi so you can use the beta testing servers. I would like to get this project underway, and would like every one to take me VERY seriously when it comes to this kind of stuff. We currently have many spots open, and would like to have them filled by Wednesday. I have no problems kicking someone off the team if they are not helping or participating. So if you get accepted, please put forth your all.
Thank you for taking time to read this, and this will be updated soon.
~Nick
[b]First Plans[/b] [code=visualfoxpro]-Come Up with a Forums Name -"project" Name [/code]
